    <Path stroke="#0076B9" d="M14 1H1v18l6.24-5.4L14 19V1Z" />
    <Path stroke="#000" strokeOpacity={0.2} d="M14 1H1v18l6.24-5.4L14 19V1Z" />

)
export default ForwardFocusSvg
